<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.9.4">
<l>eṉṉāva tettaṉai nāḷaikkup pōtum pulavīrkāṇ</l>
<l>maṉṉā maṉicaraip pāṭip paṭaikkum perumporuṇ</l>
<l>miṉṉār maṇimuṭi viṇṇavar tātaiyaip pāṭiṉā</l>
<l>ṟaṉṉāka vēkoṇṭu caṉmañcey yāmaiyuṅ koḷḷumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What is is [and] for how many tomorrows – they great wealth you create,</l>
<l>you poets, by always singing humans that do not last?</l>
<l>If you sing the father of the celestials with a crown of flashing jewels,</l>
<l>he will take [you] to be his and will undertake [you] not making [further] birth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
